## SyncConfig.initialTimestamp property

A timestamp limiting the amount of data fetched from external api. Only data created or updated after the timestamp should be included.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
initialTimestamp: number;
```

## Remarks

Setting this value will cause the system to wipe old state and resynchronize
